p accretion. We conclude that\ngravitational heating is a feasible mechanism for preventing cooling flows in\nclusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2010 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Dec 2011 09:40:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
