ating rates are computed in the optically thin\nlimit, but that the grey approximation breaks down everywhere if, as is often\ndone, the optically thick limit is assumed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2010 20:06:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Nov 2010 21:54:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-05-10"}
